claim: Ellen Burstyn was in the cast of Requiem for a Dream.
premise_source_doc_sentence: Burstyn has worked consistently in film , television , and theatre since , receiving multiple awards and nominations along the way , including seven additional Golden Globe Award nominations , five Emmy Award nominations  (  two wins  )  , and two more Academy Award for Best Actress nominations for her performances in the films Resurrection  (  1980  )  and Requiem for a Dream  (  2000  )  .
